com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.events

Interface LoadListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BrowserListener, java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoadAdapter 

    public interface LoadListener
extends BrowserListener
    The listener interface for receiving browser load events.
    用于接收浏览器加载事件的侦听器接口。

      void onDocumentLoadedInMainFrame(LoadEvent event)
      Invoked once the window.document object of the main frame was created.
      创建主框架的window.document对象后调用。

      Invoked when the provisional load was successfully committed for a specified frame.
